# Reviewable ISO 11783-6 Virtual Terminal server working-set storage fixtures.
#
# These are not CAN payloads. They lock down the local on-disk VTP1 pool-version
# cache format used by the VT server for StoreVersion / LoadVersion workflows:
# magic, timestamp_us, pool size, VT version, object count, NUL-padded classic
# label, then serialized object-pool bytes.

